The paper describes the participation of a team in a challenge related to skin lesion analysis, which involves computer vision and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning models, which suggests the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of meta-models and SVMs suggests the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the challenge involves analyzing images, which could also relate to the sub-category cs.MM (Multimedia).
